Package com.mikebull94.rsapi.bestiary

Contains classes related to the RuneScape Bestiary API.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Search.Filter
    Represents a filter that may be applied to a Search.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Beast
    Represents a beast in the RuneScape Bestiary.
    Beast.Builder  
    Bestiary
    Represents the RuneScape Bestiary API.
    Search
    Facilitates searching of the RuneScape Bestiary by applying various Search.Filters to the search.
    SearchResult
    Represents a result returned by searching within the RuneScape Bestiary.
